name: DGCP | MaMeeFarm™ — Proof 400 Empty Duck Coop — Daily Reality Record
description:
This proof records the continued absence of ducks inside the duck coop at MaMeeFarm™ on
28 December 2025, 08:07 (local time).

The image documents the physical condition of the coop:
empty ground, standing structure, and no living animals present.
No external support systems, institutional programs, or operational subsidies are involved in this moment.

This record exists to preserve unchanged reality, showing that the system remains closed,
and that progress—if any—must begin from within, not from access granted by others.

Under DGCP principles, absence is also data, and emptiness is recorded with the same integrity as activity.
